


### AdminService - Examples for Authors / Books

### 1) Search Authors by name (OData $filter)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/Authors?$filter=name%20eq%20%27Jane%20Austen%27 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=
Accept: application/json


### 2) Create an Author (returns representation when server honors Prefer: return=representation)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/Authors
Content-Type: application/json
Prefer: return=representation
Authorization: Basic <base64-credentials>  # or: Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "name": "Jane Austen",
  "dateOfBirth": "1775-12-16"
}


### 3) Create a Book linking to an Author using OData navigation binding
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/Books
Content-Type: application/json
Prefer: return=representation
Authorization: Basic <base64-credentials>  # or: Authorization: Bearer <token>

{
  "title": "Pride and Prejudice",
  "descr": "Classic novel",
  "fullText": "<trimmed or sample text>",
  "author@odata.bind": "/Authors('<AUTHOR_ID>')"
}


### 4) Helper: fetch latest author (top=1 orderby ID desc) - useful if create doesn't return ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/Authors(ed761076-2618-4c6c-9dc4-70d33334957c)
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

